                                                rdfs:subClassOf <http://schema.org/CreativeWork> ;
                                                rdf:comment "Class for interviews"@en ;
                                                rdfs:label "Interview"@nl .


###  http://data.oorlogsbronnen.nl/model#InterviewSegment
